## üîÑ Comparaison Syntaxe

### Lecture JSON

**PowerShell:**
```powershell
$content = Get-Content $file -Raw | ConvertFrom-Json
```

**Node.js:**
```javascript
const content = JSON.parse(await fs.readFile(file, 'utf8'));
// ou
const content = await readJSON(file);
```

### Glob/Pattern Matching

**PowerShell:**
```powershell
$files = Get-ChildItem -Path $path -Recurse -Filter "*.json"
```

**Node.js:**
```javascript
const files = await glob('**/*.json', { cwd: path });
// ou
const files = await findFiles('**/*.json');
```

### Logging Color√©

**PowerShell:**
```powershell
Write-Host "‚úÖ Success" -ForegroundColor Green
```

**Node.js:**
```javascript
logger.success('‚úÖ Success');
// ou
console.log('\x1b[32m‚úÖ Success\x1b[0m');
```
